<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Navigate to a class</b></p><p>To quickly open any class in the editor, press <span class="shortcut">&shortcut:GotoClass;</span> (<span class="control">Navigate | Class</span>) and start typing the name of the class. Then, click the class from the suggestion list.</p><p class="image"><img src="images/ij_tips_gotoclass.png" alt="go to class" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>